<p>
  <span class="nym">Bergamo</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Latin</span> <i>Bergomum</i>, <span class="lang">Proto-Germanic</span> <i>*bergaz</i> 'mountain', the name of an Italian city also used as a personal name.
</span>
  
</p>
  
  


